{"tid":1534912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動整合】每人每日同我做齊以下嘅事","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T07:35:23.000Z","uid":114802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b76a5b023e644207810456682fbe5eb6a8415976","tid":1534912,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"運動至今已經80幾日，香港人已經押上7條人命、1117名被捕手足，<br />\n仲有不為其數嘅受傷手足，無得再退後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFinancial Times用Water Revolution形容今次運動<br />\n水係無特定形態，同我地一樣：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理勇都只係形態，唔係分派</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同場合就用唔同形態存在，所以！<strong>每個人都係和理勇</strong>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家行動方向仲未有一致共識，但唔代表咩都唔做，事實上係有好撚多野可以做！<br />\n以下係整合呢幾日各post而成，如有遺漏，歡迎補充，及開放討論<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">未來日程，麻煩大家全力谷</span></strong></ins><br />\n<strong>9月7日 和你塞機場交通壓力測試 1300機場見 <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=9685efbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n9月8日 香港人權與民主法案集會 1400美國駐港澳領事館見</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">本地文宣</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日social media like and share 文宣post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各區連儂牆、airdrop、派街招、擺街站<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文宣source：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=47d5a23e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<a 